properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const unstretch = 200const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const flip = -(endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Limber End Controller')('Flip Art')-0.5)*2;const s0plus = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value[0];const newscale = 100+((s0plus-unstretch)/unstretch*100);const widthScale = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Limber')('Width Scale')*0.01;const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('scaleFactor').value[0];[100 * widthScale * scaleFactor * flip, newscale]

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: let val = [100, 100]if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const ctrlScaleFactor = Math.max(thisLayer.length(thisLayer.toComp([0, 0]), thisLayer.toComp([0.7071, 0.7071])), 0.0001);    val = [value[0] / ctrlScaleFactor, value[1] / ctrlScaleFactor]}val

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: let val = 0;if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const vec = thisLayer.parent.toWorldVec([1, 0, 0]);    val = -radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(vec[1], vec[0]))}val
